OL,3,CMinister plans 're-boot' of health
OL,4,Cservices reform
OL,6,FStormont's Health Minister has
OL,7,Fsignalled an intent to "re-boot" a
OL,8,Fprogramme of reform for treatment
OL,9,Fservices in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FMike Nesbitt said he would be making a
OL,12,Fseries of announcements and unveiling
OL,13,Fvarious plans across the autumn with
OL,14,Fthe aim of putting the region's health
OL,15,Fservice on a "clear path to recovery".
OL,17,FThe first of those will come on
OL,18,FTuesday when Mr Nesbitt publishes a
OL,19,Fnew framework document on
OL,20,Freconfiguring services.
