OL,6,FThe document, titled Hospitals `
OL,7,FCreating a Network for Better
OL,8,FOutcomes, will set out the rationale
OL,9,Fand guiding principles for
OL,10,Freorganising services.
OL,12,FIn a letter to MLAs, Mr Nesbitt
OL,13,Fstressed that the document would not
OL,14,Fidentify precise locations for each
OL,15,Fmedical specialty, insisting that
OL,16,Fwould require further examination.
