OL,3,CMinister plans 're-boot' of health
OL,4,Cservices reform
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt said future reconfiguration
OL,7,Fdecisions would include on emergency
OL,8,Fgeneral surgery provision in the
OL,9,FNorthern Trust area and on proposals
OL,10,Farising from a review of breast cancer
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FHe said the department also intended
OL,14,Fto publish a major independent review
OL,15,Fof maternity services in October.
OL,17,F"This autumn will be important in
OL,18,Fterms of re-booting reform and facing
OL,19,Fup to the many serious challenges
OL,20,Fahead," he wrote.
