OL,4,Cservices reform
OL,6,FThe minister also said the author of
OL,7,Fmajor blueprint for reforming health
OL,8,Fservices in Northern Ireland,
OL,9,FProfessor Rafael Bengoa, would be
OL,10,Frevisiting Northern Ireland in
OL,11,FOctober, eight years on from the
OL,12,Fpublication of his landmark report.
OL,14,FMr Nesbitt said the professor's visit
OL,15,Fwould include a keynote speech on
OL,16,FOctober 9. The minister said the
OL,17,Faddress would help "refocus attention
OL,18,Fon what needs to be done".
