OL,3,CMinister plans 're-boot' of health
OL,4,Cservices reform
OL,6,F"In the immediate weeks following
OL,7,FProfessor Bengoa's visit, I will
OL,8,Fpublish a three-year strategic plan
OL,9,Ffor the remainder of this Assembly
OL,10,Fmandate," the minister added.
OL,12,FIn his letter, Mr Nesbitt also
OL,13,Freiterated his concerns about the
OL,14,Fbudget allocation to his department.
OL,16,F"I have to say that the current
OL,17,Ffinancial position makes progress all
OL,18,Fthe more difficult," he said.
